        5/9 6:00 PM  , Perry Mets    , Granger 1     , Granger
        5/9 6:00 PM  , Granger 2     , Perry Dodgers , Perry Major
        5/13 6:00 PM , Perry Mets    , Perry Dodgers , Perry Major
        5/16 6:00 PM , Perry Dodgers , Granger 1     , Granger
        5/16 6:00 PM , Granger 2     , Perry Mets    , Perry Major
        5/20 6:00 PM , Perry Mets    , Granger 2     , Granger
